<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-8603AAE9-6C69-4ECD-B95F-EB326DB318F6" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-8603AAE9-6C69-4ECD-B95F-EB326DB318F6" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Useful SDS tests</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-7FA87A4B-7261-45A2-A3F1-4EAC9918B871"><p class="- topic/p ">The table below shows a summary of the SDS tests that can be used to analyze print quality-related issues. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">A detailed description can be found on the page of the SDS test itself. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The practical use of the SDS test in relation to a certain print quality issue is described on the page that is dedicated to the issue itself. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-A4DC4783-7F32-4C97-BFA7-99F62963A047" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">The SDS tests</title><table id="GUID-36448AD8-2662-4BA1-BB4A-FBEECE458DDE" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">SDS-test 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Purpose with respect to print quality issues 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS04-6-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-80EF4539-4481-4CD3-9E0E-62465202BFA9.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 04-6-002 Get nozzle status [Special Tests]?>04-6-002 Get nozzle status [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This test determines the amount of failing nozzles that are expected in the first swath of an image. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS04-6-035" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-BD9294C7-1B37-4EF1-930A-10559B3E3C9B.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 04-6-035 Measure differential X disturbances [Special Tests]?>04-6-035 Measure differential X disturbances [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">C1630 Only: Experimental test to determine vibrations in the engine. These vibrations might lead to OD differences in Carriage direction 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS05-6-004" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-D8F9FC25-3FC1-4E16-9980-8F702C79F676.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 05-6-004 Measure uniformity of printhead carriage speed [Special Tests]?>05-6-004 Measure uniformity of printhead carriage speed [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This test measures the uniformity of the printhead carriage speed. Deviations in speed might lead to issues in the Carriage direction. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS05-6-017" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-17F448B7-8A72-45B1-B56D-FC5C0BE28701.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 05-6-017 M&C scanner test [Special Tests]?>05-6-017 M&amp;C scanner test [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This test measures the performance of the M&amp;C-scanner. Malfunctions of the M&amp;C-scanner might lead to media step errors. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS07-6-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0B61ECEF-7439-4133-9F7C-06783020D8CF.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 07-6-002 Clean the printheads (one pulse + wipe action) [Special Tests]?>07-6-002 Clean the printheads (one pulse + wipe action) [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This test is used to clean the printheads to improve the performance of the nozzles. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS21-6-004" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-DC00B079-5A4D-415E-A896-603C50CE6C56.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-004 Measure print characteristics [Special Tests]?>21-6-004 Measure print characteristics [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">C1630 only: Experimental test to determine deviations in Y-direction 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS21-6-005" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-EC09B37A-4C4A-4AF7-8C63-0FBD950660CC.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-005 Service prints [Special Tests]?>21-6-005 Service prints [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This test is used to analyze print quality aspects 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS21-6-011" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-B8B8B2C1-FFD2-4F2F-9D12-C2BFDA22FCF5.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-011 Printhead Uniformity Test chart (PUT) [Special Tests]?>21-6-011 Printhead Uniformity Test chart (PUT) [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">This test is used to verify the print uniformity of the printheads. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="SDS21-6-012" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-2D507CB6-2FBD-4CBD-B651-16E04763526D.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-012 Printhead ink flow test chart [Special Tests]?>21-6-012 Printhead ink flow test chart [Special Tests]</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The test verifies the ink flow of the printheads 
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-61BDF02C-DCDC-4704-A599-355FCF59DF43.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Analysis Tools</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
